description:
Welcome to the Monkey House 

Kurt Vunnegut

Is an assortment of short stories written by Kurt Vonnegut, first published in August 1968. The following are two of these.

The Barnhouse Effect
A Kurt Vonnegut celebration beginning with an academic who discovers how to control the forces of nature with his mind.

The Euphio Question
Stumbling on a way to manufacture happiness presents a group of scientists with some intriguing moral and ethical dilemmas.
